## 📂 Dataset

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Source** | [UCI Machine Learning Repository](https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/phishing+websites) |
| **Total URLs** | 11,055 |
| **Features** | 30 |
| **Phishing** | 4,898 samples (-1) |
| **Suspicious** | 702 samples (0) |
| **Legitimate** | 6,157 samples (1) |
| **Train/Test Split** | 80% / 20% |

